\displaystyle \sin x + \sqrt3\cos x =0
0< x <360^\circ
\sin x+\sqrt 3\cos x=2(\sin x\times(1/2)+\cos x\times (\sqrt 3/2))=2\sin (x+60^\circ),
\sin x+\sqrt 3\cos x=0\iff \sin(x+60^\circ)=0.
0\lt x\lt 360^\circ\iff 60^\circ \lt x+60^\circ\lt 420^\circ,
x+60^\circ=180^\circ, 360^\circ.
x=120^\circ, 300^\circ.
